<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" data-theme="light">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="min-h-screen py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Header Card -->
            <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-2xl mb-6 border-t-4">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                                Raspberry Pi 6
                            </h1>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Connecté en tant que <%= user %> (<%= typeAcces %>)</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="badge badge-lg">Niveau <%= niveau %></div>
                        <!-- ...description card removed... -->
                        <div class="stat-value text-2xl">En ligne</div>
                        <div class="stat-desc">Uptime: 45 jours</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="stat-title">Température</div>
                        <div class="stat-value text-2xl">36°C</div>
                        <div class="stat-desc">Optimale</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="stat-title">CPU</div>
                        <div class="stat-value text-2xl">22%</div>
                        <div class="stat-desc">Utilisation normale</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
                        <div class="stat-title">Menaces bloquées</div>
                        <div class="stat-value text-2xl">1,247</div>
                        <div class="stat-desc">Aujourd'hui</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Description Card -->
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-2xl mb-6">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title text-2xl mb-4">Description</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                    Le Raspberry Pi 6 est dédié à la sécurité du réseau. Il agit comme pare-feu, détecte les intrusions,
                    bloque les menaces et enregistre tous les événements de sécurité. Accès réservé aux administrateurs.
                </p>
                <div class="alert mt-4">Services actifs: pfSense, Fail2Ban, Snort IDS</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Navigation Buttons -->
        <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="card-actions justify-between">
                    <a href="/dashboard?user=<%= user %>&niveau=<%= niveau %>&typeAcces=<%= typeAcces %>" class="btn btn-outline gap-2">Retour au dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline gap-2">Déconnexion</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
